snippet.textDisplay:
Biggest mistake we made was divide Punjab...Master Tara Singh should have listened to Jinnah's advice and made East Panjab an independent territory instead of joining India. Suchna huge blunder...when I see people in Pakistan, I see myself...the culture, way of life, clothing, folklore, poetry, languages, family unit etc. East Panjab is exactly the same.

One day hopefully when we form our Khalistan, our two countries will have open borders. I wish to see my Panjab and all of Pak too.
